          <title>
            <string language="sl">Kaktus - Tricocereus Pachanoi</string>
            <string language="en">Cactus - Tricocereus Pachanoi(San Pedro Cactus)</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Kaktus - Tricocereus Pachanoi(San Pedro Kaktus)</string>

            <string language="x-mt-pt">Cacto - Cacto De Tricocereus Pachanoi(San Pedro)</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Cacto - Cacto De Tricocereus Pachanoi(San Pedro)</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Kaktusi so skrivnostne rastline. Brez vode lahko zdržijo zelo dolgo. Prilagodile so se tako, da so liste spremenile v bodice, ki zelo upočasnijo izgubljanje vode.</string>
            <string language="en">The cacti are the mysterious world plant. This plants can resist without water a long time because their leaves transforms in thorns in order to keep the water as long as possible.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">kaktus</string>
            <string language="en">cactus</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">sobna rastlina</string>
            <string language="en">houseplant</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">tricocereus pachanoi</string>
            <string language="en">tricocereus pachanoi</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Kakteen sind der geheimnisvolle Weltbetrieb. 
Dieses errichtet kann ohne Wasser widerstehen eine lange Zeit, 
weil ihre Blätter in den Dornen umwandelt, um das Wasser so lang zu 
halten, wie möglich.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les cactus sont l'usine mystérieuse du monde. 
Ceci plante peut résister sans eau un long temps parce que 
leurs feuilles transforme dans des épines afin de maintenir l'eau 
aussi longue comme possible.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os cactos são a planta misteriosa do mundo. 
Isto planta pode resistir sem água uma estadia longa porque 
suas folhas transformam nos espinhos a fim manter a água tão longa 
como possível.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I cactus sono la pianta mysterious del mondo. 
Ciò pianta può resistere a senza acqua un molto tempo perché 
i loro fogli trasforma in spine per mantenere l'acqua lunga come 
possibile.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Οι κάκτοι είναι οι μυστήριες παγκόσμιες 
εγκαταστάσεις. Αυτά τα φυτά μπορούν να αντισταθούν χωρίς 
ύδωρ σε έναν μακροχρόνιο χρόνο επειδή οι μετατροπές φύλλων τους
στα αγκάθια προκειμένου να κρατηθεί το ύδωρ καθ' όσο είναι 
δυνατό.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Los cactos son la planta misteriosa del mundo. 
Esto planta puede resistir sin el agua un rato largo porque sus 
hojas transforman en espinas para mantener el agua tan larga como sea 
posible.</string>
          </description>
